Preheat oven to 300 degrees F (150 degrees C). In a medium bowl, mix the cream cheese, milk, onion, horseradish, salt, pepper and crabmeat. Spread the mixture into a pie pan or shallow baking dish. Sprinkle almonds over the crabmeat mixture Bake in the preheated oven 45 minutes, or until bubbly and lightly browned.